creator: LETS FUN - publisher of match 3 puzzle game
descriptionHtml:
One of the most addictive puzzle game on mobile today! You can get free rewards and boosters through this amazing adventure!

You can play Candy house Smash at anytime and anywhere. It will be fine if without Wi-Fi.

🌈How to play🌈
1. At each level, you have a specific list of goals, just complete them before you run out of moves and then you will be rewarded with unexpected prizes
2. Switch two elements next to each other in order to get three or more similar gems in a row to smash them
3. Coins are important. You can use them to buy powerful boosters

🌈Features🌈
1. Puzzle match games with hundreds of levels
2. It is a totally FREE tasty candy game
3. Beautiful and lovely graphics
4. Easy to play, but still takes skills to master!
5. Solve puzzles by using and combining special boosters and power-ups
6. Battle it out in Global Multiplayer Tournaments for the chance of being crowned the Ultimate Winner
7. You can play while offline (no Internet connection required)
8. Our dedicated team is working hard to create fresh new content for you
